OL,3,CConsumer confidence stabilises as Gen
OL,4,CZ prepares to spend
OL,6,FConsumer confidence has stabilised
OL,7,Fafter February's record low amid
OL,8,Fpredictions by Gen Z that they are
OL,9,Fready to increase their spending,
OL,10,Ffigures show.
OL,12,FConsumer expectations for the state of
OL,13,Fthe economy over the next three months
OL,14,Fimproved slightly, but remains at
OL,15,Fminus 35, according to British Retail
OL,16,FConsortium (BRC)-Opinium data.
