OL,4,CZ prepares to spend
OL,6,FExpectations for consumers' personal
OL,7,Ffinancial situations also improved,
OL,8,Falbeit to minus 10, while confidence
OL,9,Fin personal spending on retail rose to
OL,10,Fa relatively healthy zero, up from
OL,11,Fminus five last month, driven by plans
OL,12,Ffor DIY and home improvements.
OL,14,FGen Z ` those aged 18 to 27 ` expect
OL,15,Fto spend more than the previous three
OL,16,Fmonths in every category, while Gen X
OL,17,F` 44 to 59 year olds ` are planning
OL,18,Fthe biggest cuts to spending for most
OL,19,Fitems except for food, the poll found.
