OL,3,CConsumer confidence stabilises as Gen
OL,4,CZ prepares to spend
OL,6,FBRC chief executive Helen Dickinson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Consumer confidence stabilised
OL,8,Fthis month after February's record
OL,9,Flow. This was coupled with an increase
OL,10,Fin spending expectations for the three
OL,11,Fmonths ahead, both for retail spending
OL,12,Fand spending more generally.
OL,14,F"The spring statement is an
OL,15,Fopportunity for Government to inject
OL,16,Fsome confidence back into the economy.
